                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1353" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0248</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8134 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">做好事就有好报吗？——铭星电子验厂反思</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">无</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">周二华，邵丹萍</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华中科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">铭星电子公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR验厂；新生代员工；离职</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR audits；new generation employees；employee turnover</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在经济全球化的今天，企业承担社会责任，对内有利于提高员工满意度和归属感，对外则有利于提升企业声誉和市场竞争力。案例企业铭星电子公司是多家品牌电子产品的供应商，因其上游客户就生产中存在污染、侵犯和毒害等伤害劳工权益事件而处于公众广泛质疑和谴责的危机下，被动实施企业社会责任（Cooperate Social Responsibility, CSR）并接受第三方验厂。但公司发现，尽管他们投入了大量财力、物力和人力资源进行了内部CSR活动，如工作场所的改造、升级，员工工作生活条件和福利待遇的改善与提高，并最终顺利通过了验厂，但员工的满意度和归属感却并未有所改善和提高，员工离职率依然居高不下，尤其是新生代员工的离职问题更显突出。本案例一方面可以启发人们思考电子代工企业应该如何正确认识及履行CSR；另一方面也激发人们思考如何实施CSR，才能有效提高员工的满意度和忠诚度，留住员工。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the impact of enterprise development on society and the business   increasing, there is a rising appeal for corporate social responsibility. In today&#39;s economic globalization, corporate social responsibility not only helps to improve employee satisfaction and sense of belonging internally, but also enhances corporate reputation and market competitiveness externally. This case describes the Mingxing Electronics Company, as a supplier of branded electronic products, was forced to implement corporate social responsibility. This is because its upstream client was widely questioned and condemned for pollution and the violation of labor rights in the production, which brought it into a crisis. Moreover, despite Mingxing company invested a lot of resources in internal CSR activities and successfully passed the audit, employee satisfaction and their sense of belonging have not been improved. This can be reflected in the high turnover rate, especially among the new generation staff. On one hand, this case can inspire us to think about how enterprises should understand and fulfill the CSR correctly. On the other hand, it has shed light on how to take advantage of CSR to retain employees when the employee turnover rate of new generation remains high.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2012</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">社会责任</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013-10</td>
                            </tr>
